##  DEPLOY COMPLETO (Automatico)

**Eseguire da:** `C:\Dev\MESManager`

```powershell
# STEP 1: Modifica versione in MESManager.Web/Components/Layout/MainLayout.razor (linea ~126)
# Cambia: v1.11  v1.12 (oppure v1.12  v1.13, ecc.)

# STEP 2: BUILD
Write-Host " Building..." -ForegroundColor Cyan
dotnet build MESManager.sln -c Release --nologo > $null 2>&1

# STEP 3: PUBLISH
Write-Host " Publishing..." -ForegroundColor Cyan
dotnet publish MESManager.Web/MESManager.Web.csproj -c Release -o publish/Web --nologo > $null 2>&1

# STEP 4: STOP
Write-Host " Stopping app..." -ForegroundColor Cyan
taskkill /S 192.168.1.230 /U Administrator /P "A123456!" /IM MESManager.Web.exe /F 2>$null
Start-Sleep 2

# STEP 5: COPY (escludi config sensibili)
Write-Host " Copying files..." -ForegroundColor Cyan
robocopy "C:\Dev\MESManager\publish\Web" "\\192.168.1.230\c$\MESManager" /E /XF appsettings.Secrets.json appsettings.Database.json *.log *.pdb /XD logs SyncBackups > $null 2>&1

# STEP 6: RESTART
Write-Host " Starting app..." -ForegroundColor Cyan
schtasks /S 192.168.1.230 /U Administrator /P "A123456!" /Run /TN "StartMESWeb" 2>$null
Start-Sleep 6

# STEP 7: VERIFY
tasklist /S 192.168.1.230 /U Administrator /P "A123456!" | findstr MES
Write-Host " Deploy completato! http://192.168.1.230:5156  Ctrl+Shift+R" -ForegroundColor Green
```

---

##  Deploy Solo JS (senza recompile)

```powershell
Copy-Item "C:\Dev\MESManager\MESManager.Web\wwwroot\lib\ag-grid\*.js" "\\192.168.1.230\c$\MESManager\wwwroot\lib\ag-grid\" -Force
Write-Host " JS aggiornati - Utenti: Ctrl+Shift+R"
```

---

##  Versioning

Prima di deploy, modifica versione in `MESManager.Web/Components/Layout/MainLayout.razor`:
```html
v1.12  <!-- Incrementa: v1.11  v1.12  v1.13 ... -->
```

Poi aggiorna `docs/CHANGELOG.md` con cosa è cambiato.
